  "title": "Devotional: The Threat of Self",
  "body": "The most dangerous part of this path for me is the threat of self. It is so easy to find yourself wise. To believe that any of this is the result of self.\n\nThe only thing to do is die to self. Give control to one greater. Submit to the yoke.\n\nAll power is His. All greatness is His. His mercy provides life everlasting.",
